

Server
PORT=8000
NODE_ENV=development
URL of the frontend dev server, used for CORS in app.js
CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:5173

MySQL database — point these at YOUR OWN local MySQL instance
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_PORT=3306
DB_NAME=hms_db
DB_USER=root
DB_PASSWORD=your_local_mysql_password

JWT secrets — generate your own random strings, do NOT reuse someone else's.
Quick way to generate one: `node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(48).toString('hex'))"`
JWT_ACCESS_SECRET=replace_with_a_long_random_string
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=replace_with_a_different_long_random_string
